<view class="page analytics-page"><page-state wx:if="{{loading}}" type="loading" title="正在汇总今日订单" /><page-state wx:elif="{{error}}" type="error" title="营业数据加载失败" description="{{error}}" action-text="重试" bind:action="load" /><block wx:else><view class="analytics-hero"><view class="analytics-hero__label">今日订单总数</view><view class="analytics-hero__value">{{total}}<text> 单</text></view></view><view class="metric-grid analytics-grid"><view class="metric"><view class="metric__value">{{waiting}}</view><view class="metric__label">待接单</view></view><view class="metric"><view class="metric__value">{{preparing}}</view><view class="metric__label">制作中</view></view><view class="metric"><view class="metric__value">{{waitingRider}}</view><view class="metric__label">待骑手</view></view><view class="metric"><view class="metric__value">{{completed}}</view><view class="metric__label">已完成</view></view></view><view class="card notice"><view class="notice__title">数据口径</view><view class="subtitle">本页仅通过商家订单分页接口的真实 total 汇总今日订单数量。当前后端没有营业额、结算、库存预警专用接口，因此不展示估算金额，也不声称为财务数据。</view></view></block></view>
